author: Ben Kamisar, Melissa Holzberg
title: Senate campaigns raise big money ahead of possible coronavirus crunch
description: A Senate Democratic challenger outraised a Republican incumbent in six of the 10 most competitive races rated by Cook Political Report (where a Republican incumbent is running for reelection).
content:
